 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-bowe","title":"Implement critical inline CSS for offline-first rendering","description":"# Task: Critical Inline CSS

## Context
The HTML export must be fully functional offline. This means critical styles must be
embedded directly in the HTML file, providing a complete visual experience without
any network requests.

## Design Philosophy
Following the progressive enhancement model:
1. **Offline-First**: All essential styles inline
2. **CDN Enhancement**: Tailwind adds polish when available
3. **Print-Ready**: @media print rules for PDF export
4. **Theme Support**: CSS variables for dark/light modes

## Deliverables

### 1. CSS Variable System (src/html_export/styles.rs)
```css
:root {
    /* Base palette from TUI theme.rs */
    --bg-deep: #1a1b26;
    --bg-surface: #24283b;
    --bg-highlight: #292e42;
    --border: #3b4261;
    --border-focus: #7d91c8;

    /* Text hierarchy */
    --text-primary: #c0caf5;
    --text-secondary: #a9b1d6;
    --text-muted: #696e9e;

    /* Accents */
    --accent: #7aa2f7;
    --accent-secondary: #bb9af7;

    /* Role colors */
    --role-user: #9ece6a;
    --role-agent: #7aa2f7;
    --role-tool: #ff9e64;
    --role-system: #e0af68;

    /* Status */
    --success: #73daca;
    --warning: #e0af68;
    --error: #f7768e;
}

[data-theme="light"] {
    --bg-deep: #f5f5f5;
    --bg-surface: #ffffff;
    /* ... light mode overrides */
}
```

### 2. Layout Classes
- Container with max-width and padding
- Conversation message bubbles (user right-aligned, agent left-aligned)
- Header with metadata section
- Toolbar with search and controls
- Code block styling with overflow scroll
- Collapsible sections for tool calls

### 3. Typography
- System font stack for fast loading
- Monospace for code (JetBrains Mono via CDN, fallback to system)
- Proper line heights for readability
- Responsive font sizing

### 4. Component Styles
```css
/* Message bubble base */
.message {
    max-width: 85%;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.message-user {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--role-user);
    margin-left: auto;
}

.message-agent {
    background: var(--bg-highlight);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--role-agent);
}

/* Code blocks */
.code-block {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
}

/* Collapsible tool calls */
.tool-call > summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
}
```

### 5. Print Styles
```css
@media print {
    body { background: white; color: black; }
    .no-print { display: none; }
    .message { page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .code-block { white-space: pre-wrap; }
    a { text-decoration: underline; }
    a[href]::after { content: " (" attr(href) ")"; }
}
```

### 6. Responsive Design
- Mobile-first breakpoints
- Touch-friendly targets (44px minimum)
- Readable on all screen sizes

