- Replace generic STYLE_TEXT_PRIMARY usage in active-pill rendering with semantic token-driven chip styling.
- Refactor pill rendering so each active pill is rendered as its own styled span/chip unit.
- Preserve existing click-target geometry and interaction behavior (last_pill_rects) exactly.

## Explicit Decision
- Whole-row background styling can be used only as a short-lived intermediate spike.
- Definition of done requires per-pill chip styling (individual chip backgrounds), not a row-level approximation.

